                <div class="row gx-4 gx-lg-5 justify-content-center">
                    <div class="col-md-10 col-lg-8 col-xl-7">
                        <div class="post-heading">
                            <h1>Here will be an image or a slideshow or related to </h1>
                            <h2 class="subheading">a news api or just some random chart video</h2>
